@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml

title Fencing Token 二期扩展组件图

left to right direction
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide empty members

package "API" {
  class LockOptions
  interface LockHandle
  class LockResult
  class FencingTokenGuard
}

package "Core Fencing" {
  class FencingTokenCoordinator
  class FencingTokenPlan
  enum FencingTokenMode {
    NONE
    NATIVE
    EXTERNAL
  }
  interface FencingTokenProvider
  interface FencingTokenProviderRegistry
  class DefaultFencingTokenProviderRegistry
  class FencingTokenRequest
  class FencingTokenResponse
}

package "Lock Provider" {
  interface LockProvider
  class RedisLockProvider
}

package "External Fencing Provider" {
  class JdbcSequenceFencingTokenProvider
  class JdbcFencingTokenSchemaInitializer
}

package "Business Resource" {
  class FencedRepository
  database BusinessDB
}

LockOptions --> FencingTokenCoordinator : fencingRequired\nproviderName
FencingTokenCoordinator --> FencingTokenPlan : select
FencingTokenPlan --> FencingTokenMode
FencingTokenCoordinator --> LockProvider : inspect capabilities
FencingTokenCoordinator --> FencingTokenProviderRegistry : select external
DefaultFencingTokenProviderRegistry ..|> FencingTokenProviderRegistry
FencingTokenProviderRegistry o-- FencingTokenProvider
JdbcSequenceFencingTokenProvider ..|> FencingTokenProvider
RedisLockProvider ..|> LockProvider
JdbcFencingTokenSchemaInitializer --> BusinessDB : create token table
JdbcSequenceFencingTokenProvider --> BusinessDB : increment token row
LockHandle --> FencingTokenGuard : token
FencingTokenGuard --> FencedRepository : conditional write
FencedRepository --> BusinessDB : last_fencing_token < token
LockResult --> LockHandle

note bottom of FencingTokenCoordinator
  选择顺序：
  1. 未要求 -> NONE
  2. 显式 redis -> NATIVE
  3. 显式 jdbc-sequence -> EXTERNAL
  4. 未显式时优先锁 Provider 原生能力
  5. 无原生能力时使用唯一外部 Provider
end note

note bottom of FencedRepository
  Fencing 的最终安全边界在业务资源。
  只生成 token 而不做条件更新没有保护作用。
end note

@enduml
